OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy and mostly dry until mid-
OL,6,Fafternoon with brighter intervals.
OL,7,FPerhaps a few showers in the west.
OL,8,FShowers becoming more widespread from
OL,9,Fmid-afternoon, ahead of a band of very
OL,10,Fheavy rain and strong gusts moving
OL,11,Fsouth, reaching northern parts by dusk.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy, gusty rain band
OL,14,Fclearing south by midnight. Clear
OL,15,Fspells and wintry showers follow, and
OL,16,Fturning colder with perhaps some brief
OL,17,Fsnow over hills. Some patchy frost
OL,18,Fpossible by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
