OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F167A1773667690
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FOften cloudy in the north,
OL,6,Fwith brighter or sunny spells further
OL,7,Fsouth. Occasional showers possible,
OL,8,Fbut largely falling as rain for all
OL,9,Fexcept the highest hills. Chilly,
OL,10,Fdespite easing winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFine
OL,13,FSaturday, with brighter or sunny
OL,14,Fspells, light winds, and isolated
OL,15,Fshowers. Rain spreading east Sunday,
OL,16,Fthen colder again with showers
OL,17,Ffollowing, wintry over hills. Breezy,
OL,18,Fbut mostly dry Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
